==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Regrant
<hw>Re*grant"</hw> <pr>(r?*gr?nt")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To grant
back; to grant again or anew.</def> <rj><au>Ayliffe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Regrant</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Regrant
<hw>Re*grant"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of granting
back to a former proprietor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A renewed of a grant; <as>as, the <ex>regrant</ex>
of a monopoly</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Regrate</ent>⟦br⟧
